{
  "texts": [
    "c 2: The dataset inputs must be realistic.",
    "c 3: Task instances require a notable effort from people, or people are bad at them.",
    "An application must exist if the goal is to evaluate the usefulness of explanations within the context of human-AI interaction for that application.",
    "For example, COMMONSENSEQA (Talmor et al., 2019), one of the most popular datasets in NLP explainability research, has no associated application as people do not need answers to questions such as \"At the end of your meal what will a waiter do?",
    "serve food, eat, set table, serve meal, or present bill\"."
  ]
}